==================================================


LOOPS SUMMARY

for - do - done 			##perform a set of commands for each item in a list
while - done				##perform a set of commands while a test is true
until - do - done			##perform a set of commands until a test is true
break						##exit the current loop
continue					##stop current iteratio of the loop and begin the next iteration








